,"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"composed of multiple vertices."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPoint"}],"title":"MLNMultiPoint","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapsho